{"tid":837772,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【習總南巡】傳下月出席港珠澳大橋通車 料參觀香港口岸","createTime":"2018-09-26T15:24:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-27T11:16:46.000Z","uid":212249,"like":1,"dislike":40,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"41e6eddce27c1df58e375a7dddc4e7eff43684a2","tid":837772,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T15:24:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180926/large/1537973582_15e8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180926%2Flarge%2F1537973582_15e8.jpg&h=5aba67e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港納稅人支付上千億公帑興建的港珠澳大橋，預計在下月通車，有報道指中央高度重視，國家主席習近平、國務院總理李克強等領導人，將會專程南下，出席大橋的通車儀式。<br />\n<br />\n香港《南華早報》引述消息指出，香港、澳門、珠海三地的官員，後日起將會一連三日會舉行演習，以確保三地通關暢順。報道引述消息指國家領導人將南下出席在珠海舉行的通車儀式，除習近平、李克強之外，主管港澳事務的副總理韓正亦會出席。<br />\n<br />\n報道又指出，在通車儀式之後，一眾國家領導人將會坐車通過大橋前往香港，預計參觀通過香港機場外人工島的香港口岸，但不會進入香港市中心，亦不會在香港過夜。<br />\n<br />\n月前香港、澳門及珠海政府已經確定大橋10月通車，通車儀式將在珠海舉行。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180926/58727534\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180926%2F58727534&d=bXVSS1kgvuXGrx8aV44%2B0U%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=d4e41033\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180926%2F58727534&h=05147ab9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180926/58727534</a>"},{"pid":"b4b8ae76c1920be6a87f9f89d3e59db9aa842326","tid":837772,"uid":45914,"like":48,"dislike":0,"score":48,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T15:27:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a05628c19b8580d8163d847a8ae53094e52d40af","tid":837772,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T15:29:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0317daf29d352e636740d086d4b6f435e83d51c